title: The Common Linnets 2016-06-10 Pinkpop Holland
description:
Here is a nice Pinkpop broadcast. Check my account for more classic bootlegs. 

Please enjoy, share with friends and please seed :)

The Common Linnets
Pinkpop, Megaland, Landgraaf, The Netherlands
June 10, 2016
Main Stage 16:25-17:25

Setlist not available (help is appreciated, thanks in advance). Their 2015 Eurovision hitsong Calm After The Storm is played last.

The first two songs of the show were not broadcast. No permission was given at the last minute. Also when this was replayed later last night and this morning, both the first track as well as the second to last track of this original broadcast were left out. The latter can be noticed as in one shot Ilse de Lange is holding a guitar, while in the other only a microphone ;-)

Taken from the Dutch national television channel NPO Cultura broadcast, June 10, 2016.

Lineage : NPO Cultura DVB-C - Humax iHDR-5050C - VideoReDo TVSuite 4.20.7.629
